invalid type: string "{\"raw_text\": \"3.2 Attention\\n\\nAn attention function can be described as mapping a query and a set of key-value pairs to an output, where the query, keys, values, and output are all vectors. The output is computed as a weighted sum\\n\\n3\\n\\nScaled Dot-Product Attention\\n\\nMulti-Head Attention\\n\\nLinear\\n\\nFigure 2: (left) Scaled Dot-Product Attention. (right) Multi-Head Attention consists of several attention layers running in parallel.\\n\\nof the values, where the weight assigned to each value is computed by a compatibility function of the query with the corresponding key.\", \"tables_html\": [], \"images_base64\": [\"\", \"\"]}", expected a "]}\"]}","doc_id":"23162748-bd63-418b-a0b2-8312ec833a87","chunk_index":4,"source":"attention-is-all-you-need.pdf"}␀␀␀M␀␀␀yM␀␀␀ÉńxM␀␀␀0yM␀␀␀░FyM␀␀␀PyM␀␀␀­FyM␀␀␀pyM␀␀␀0GyM␀␀␀ÉyM␀␀␀pGyM␀␀␀░yM␀␀␀└ńxM␀␀␀ąyM␀␀␀░GyM␀␀␀­yM␀␀␀­GyM␀␀␀yM␀␀␀0HyM␀␀␀0yM␀␀␀­ńxM␀␀␀PyM␀␀␀pHyM␀␀␀pyM␀␀␀ ĶxM␀␀␀ÉyM␀␀␀PĶxM␀␀␀░yM␀␀␀░HyM␀␀␀ąyM␀␀␀­HyM␀␀␀­yM␀␀␀ĆĶxM␀␀␀yM␀␀␀░ĶxM␀␀␀0yM␀␀␀ÓĶxM␀␀␀PyM␀␀␀ķxM␀␀␀pyM␀␀␀@ķxM␀␀␀ÉyM␀␀␀pķxM␀␀␀░yM␀␀␀ĀķxM␀␀␀ąyM␀␀␀0IyM␀␀␀­yM␀␀␀pIyM␀␀␀yM␀␀␀ąķxM␀␀␀0yM␀␀␀␀ĻxM␀␀␀PyM␀␀␀0ĻxM␀␀␀pyM␀␀␀░IyM␀␀␀ÉyM␀␀␀`ĻxM␀␀␀░yM␀␀␀­IyM␀␀␀ąyM␀␀␀ÉĻxM␀␀␀­yM␀␀␀0JyM␀␀␀yM␀␀␀pJyM␀␀␀0yM␀␀␀└ĻxM␀␀␀PyM␀␀␀­ĻxM␀␀␀pyM␀␀␀ ļxM␀␀␀ÉyM␀␀␀░JyM␀␀␀░yM␀␀␀PļxM␀␀␀ąyM␀␀␀­JyM␀␀␀­yM␀␀␀ĆļxM␀␀␀yM␀␀␀░ļxM␀␀␀0yM␀␀␀ÓļxM␀␀␀PyM␀␀␀ņxM␀␀␀pyM␀␀␀@ņxM␀␀␀ÉyM␀␀␀pņxM␀␀␀░yM␀␀␀ĀņxM␀␀␀ąyM␀␀␀0KyM␀␀␀­yM␀␀␀ąņxM␀␀␀yM␀␀␀pKyM␀␀␀0yM␀␀␀␀ĒxM␀␀␀PyM␀␀␀0ĒxM␀␀␀pyM␀␀␀`ĒxM␀␀␀ÉyM␀␀␀░KyM␀␀␀░yM␀␀␀░j$M␀␀␀ąyM␀␀␀­KyM␀␀␀­yM␀␀␀0LyM␀␀␀yM␀␀␀pLyM␀␀␀0yM␀␀␀ÉĒxM␀␀␀PyM␀␀␀└ĒxM␀␀␀pyM␀␀␀­ĒxM␀␀␀ÉyM␀␀␀░LyM␀␀␀░yM␀␀␀ ŅxM␀␀␀ąyM␀␀␀­LyM␀␀␀­yM␀␀␀PŅxM␀␀␀yM␀␀␀ĆŅxM␀␀␀0yM␀␀␀░ŅxM␀␀␀PyM␀␀␀ÓŅxM␀␀␀pyM␀␀␀’xM␀␀␀ÉyM␀␀␀@’xM␀␀␀░yM␀␀␀0MyM␀␀␀ąyM␀␀␀pMyM␀␀␀­yM␀␀␀p’xM␀␀␀yM␀␀␀Ā’xM␀␀␀0yM␀␀␀ą’xM␀␀␀PyM␀